{{!-- English --}}
<div lang="en">
  <p class="lead"><strong>YourExpo2015</strong> is the challenge launched by Expo on life, food and its perception.</p>

  <p class="lead">Be ready to be challenged every week by two new topics or dimensions about food.</p>

  <p class="lead">You can partecipate by posting on Instagram your photos about one of the two topics of the week, tagging it with the official hashtag.</p>

  <p class="lead">The most popular photos will be added to the challenge gallery and will be promoted using the official EXPO social channels.</p>
</div>


{{!-- Italian --}}
